      steps:['Between each delivery: drop both shoulders and breathe out slowly','Take one slow breath: in for 4 counts, hold for 1, out for 6','During the exhale: consciously release grip from 7+ back to 4','Eyes forward, chin down, weight 50/50','Take your stance and wait for the bowler','Repeat this routine for 20 consecutive shadow balls, rating tension 1–10 after each'],
      keyFocus:'Breathe out — drop the tension', commonError:'Skipping the routine under pressure — exactly when it is most needed.',
