      steps:['Set up: 2 slip cones and gully cone in fielding positions','Bowl 30-ball powerplay simulation — full outswing corridor','After each 6 balls: review how many achieved all 3 criteria (swing + length + line)','Track: which criterion did you fail most?','Bowl extra targeted reps on the weakest criterion','Target 10/20 "perfect" by end of session'],
      keyFocus:'Swing + length + line — all three at once', commonError:'Chasing swing and forgetting length — half-volley outswinger is still a half-volley',
