      steps:['Mark the wide line with tape','Bowl 20 deliveries targeting outside-off stump area','Lives game: 3 lives — each actual wide costs a life','Score a point for each in-corridor delivery (12 target)','Identify: are you missing wide or too straight? Fix accordingly','Run the drill until 12/20 in corridor with zero wides'],
