      videoId:'PLACEHOLDER', videoChannel:'Cricket Australia', videoTitle:'Off-Stump Bouncer',
      outcome:'The off-stump bouncer creates genuine edge and false-shot opportunities that the body-line bouncer does not.',
      fit:{ roles:['pace-opener','pace-death','all-rounder'], goals:['technical','team-selection'], ages:['u19','senior'], phases:['middle-overs','death-overs'], surfaces:['bouncy','all'], formats:['test','odi','all'] },
      steps:['Target: short delivery, line at off-stump, carrying to shoulder height','Bowl 15 deliveries targeting this combination','Partner tracks: line / height / are both correct?','Count balls where line AND height are both correct','If mostly body-line: shift target; if too short or too full: adjust length','Target 8/15 correct combination'],
