      steps:['Set target: 80 runs off 10 overs to defend','Bowl with the explicit goal of dot balls — not wickets','Resist any change in plan when the batter takes a risk','Track runs per over — is the rate staying below 7.5?','Note: wickets happen from the pressure, not from risk-bowling','Debrief: which overs went above 7.5 and why?'],
