      steps:['Set up both ends of the pitch','Field ball from various ring positions (cover, mid-on, mid-off, point)','Throw to the bowler\'s end stumps','Score a point for each on-target throw (7 target)','Repeat with throw to keeper\'s end for comparison','Identify which end is less accurate and drill it'],
