      steps:['Audio cue triggers left dive','Drive off the right foot sideways — leading with the left hand','Land on the outside of the left arm (not the hand/wrist)','10 dive attempts to the left','Count clean ball collections during the dive','Compare to right-side dive accuracy — drill the weaker side'],
