      steps:['Establish your current fielding stats across 5 matches (self-assessment)','Compare to elite benchmarks: drop rate, runs saved, direct hit attempts','Identify your biggest gap from elite standards','Design a specific 4-week training program targeting that gap','Re-assess after 4 weeks — did the metric improve?','Continue the cycle: measure, identify gap, drill, re-measure'],
