      videoId:'PLACEHOLDER', videoChannel:'Cricket Australia', videoTitle:'Wicketkeeper Weight Transfer for Pace',
      outcome:'Balance for pace keeping is consistent — wide balls and rises are reachable from the balanced starting position.',
