      videoId:'PLACEHOLDER', videoChannel:'Cricket Australia', videoTitle:'Wicketkeeping to Off-Spin',
      outcome:'Mixed off-spin deliveries are taken cleanly — arm balls and top-spinners are as reliable as standard off-breaks.',
      fit:{ roles:['wicketkeeper'], goals:['technical','team-selection'], ages:['u15','u17','u19','senior'], phases:['all'], surfaces:['all'], formats:['all'] },
      steps:['Partner bowls mixed off-spin: off-break / arm ball / top-spinner','Gloves: neutral — do not pre-set for the off-break turn','React after pitching for off-breaks; arm balls go straight','Count clean takes across all types','Identify weakest variation and drill it separately','Target 7/10 mixed clean takes'],
