      steps:['Partner throws balls with a mid-flight direction change (using a bent or cut ball)','Track: start of flight → see the deviation → adjust gloves','10 attempts — 3 lives, each miss costs a life','Count successful adjustments (6 target)','Key: do not commit fully until deviation is confirmed','Discuss: how early can you read the deviation?'],
      keyFocus:'Track the deviation — adjust mid-movement', commonError:'Fully committing to initial trajectory — the deviation catches committed gloves out of position',
