      steps:["Receive each ball with relaxed fingers pointing down and in, letting the glove \"give\" backward on contact","Keep elbows soft and slightly bent — never locked out at the moment of the take","Bring the ball in towards the body immediately after the take, don't snatch at it","Repeat at three heights: waist, chest, head — soft hands matter at every height","Track drops vs clean takes each set — aim for zero two-handed snatches"],
