      steps:['Start with bodyweight or light dumbbells — master the movement first','Hinge at hips (not knees): push hips backward as hands lower toward floor','Back must stay flat — not curved or rounded','Hands lower to just below knee — feel hamstring stretch','Drive hips forward to return to standing (not pulling with lower back)','Film side-on: check back position throughout movement'],
